      <p>If you want to get in touch with us, collaborate with us, joint the platform, anything really, drop us a line and we will make sure to contact you.</p>

      <p><strong>loyalty.berlin@gmail.com</strong></p>

      <p>Thanks and Cheers </p>
    </section>
  </div>
